1
00:00:00,490 --> 00:00:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That legend...</font>

2
00:00:05,810 --> 00:00:07,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was about us.</font>

3
00:00:12,320 --> 00:00:14,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember now?</font>

4
00:00:15,240 --> 00:00:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Sooha's been connected 
to us since long ago.</font>

5
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:20,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

6
00:00:21,330 --> 00:00:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why we've been 
drawn to her since we met.</font>

7
00:00:25,120 --> 00:00:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Marge was protecting us from Dardan.</font>

8
00:00:30,110 --> 00:00:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jakah, can you detect Sooha's energy?</font>

9
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I can't.</font>

10
00:00:37,480 --> 00:00:40,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are only two reasons someone's 
energy would weaken this much.</font>

11
00:00:41,110 --> 00:00:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're either unconscious 
or... no longer living.</font>

12
00:00:46,980 --> 00:00:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was I doing?</font>

13
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:52,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was supposed to protect Sooha.</font>

14
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:54,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go to Vanfield House.</font>

15
00:00:57,910 --> 00:01:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan may come for an object there.</font>

16
00:01:02,390 --> 00:01:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What object?</font>

17
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vionys, a scroll on the Vargr Kingdom.</font>

18
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vionys...</font>

19
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kingdom fell long ago, 
and only a few were told its secrets.</font>

20
00:01:16,430 --> 00:01:21,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan needs those secrets 
to acquire power.</font>

21
00:01:31,820 --> 00:01:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never thought I'd see you again.</font>

22
00:01:35,830 --> 00:01:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The princess must've brought us together.</font>

23
00:01:39,780 --> 00:01:41,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know Sooha is alive.</font>

24
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll find and rescue her no matter what.</font>

25
00:03:11,060 --> 00:03:16,960
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}<font size="30">- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</font></b></font>

26
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:21,970
<font face="Times New Roman" size="23" color="#f9fcfd"><b><font size="23">- The Black Mist of Railgun -</font></b></font>

27
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels so strange to 
return to this place.</font>

28
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Voluntarily, too.</font>

29
00:03:56,610 --> 00:03:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vionys is gone!</font>

30
00:03:58,830 --> 00:04:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're too late.</font>

31
00:04:00,210 --> 00:04:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, he could still be inside the mansion.</font>

32
00:04:03,790 --> 00:04:04,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's split up.</font>

33
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:06,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll search the bedrooms.</font>

34
00:04:06,770 --> 00:04:08,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll check the third floor.</font>

35
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:26,660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Guys, come to the lounge!</i></font>

36
00:04:30,930 --> 00:04:31,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jakah!</font>

37
00:04:32,770 --> 00:04:34,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This was the only one still here.</font>

38
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jaan caught him.</font>

39
00:04:36,930 --> 00:04:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

40
00:04:38,340 --> 00:04:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't sense Marge inside the mansion.</font>

41
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me...</font>

42
00:04:49,010 --> 00:04:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did you take Marge?!</font>

43
00:04:51,850 --> 00:04:53,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did Dardan put you up to this?</font>

44
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:55,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did your allies go?!</font>

45
00:04:56,690 --> 00:04:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll try asking him.</font>

46
00:04:59,650 --> 00:05:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did you take Sooha and Marge?</font>

47
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did you take the scroll you stole?</font>

48
00:05:12,530 --> 00:05:13,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Answer me!</font>

49
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Printanier...</font>

50
00:05:18,620 --> 00:05:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Printanier?</font>

51
00:05:20,130 --> 00:05:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's pretty far from here.</font>

52
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's in Printanier?</font>

53
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Dardan there, too?</font>

54
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:54,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fool. I should've killed him right away.</font>

55
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:57,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter. I'll figure it out.</font>

56
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, we will become one.</font>

57
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those with shaman's blood have 
ruled this kingdom for generations.</font>

58
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When a ruler left the throne,</font>

59
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they sealed all their power 
inside the moon altar,</font>

60
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and on the night of a full moon,</font>

61
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the next ruler inherited 
their power through a ritual.</font>

62
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When the moon is full, that altar's 
seal will be broken thanks to you.</font>

63
00:06:32,150 --> 00:06:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I will inherit that power 
and become the new king.</font>

64
00:06:39,290 --> 00:06:43,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The last thing I need is Vargr's blood.</font>

65
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, everything will be mine.</font>

66
00:06:56,680 --> 00:07:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Despite my family's downfall, I rose 
to become chancellor of this kingdom.</i></font>

67
00:07:05,230 --> 00:07:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So what could I possibly be lacking?</i></font>

68
00:07:14,910 --> 00:07:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Beautiful Selen, I will make you mine!</i></font>

69
00:07:38,060 --> 00:07:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The blood of Vargr!</font>

70
00:07:42,490 --> 00:07:45,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan! What are you doing there?</font>

71
00:07:46,930 --> 00:07:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get away from Vionys!</font>

72
00:07:51,890 --> 00:07:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only royals are permitted to read this!</font>

73
00:07:55,450 --> 00:07:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Status, status, status! This again?</font>

74
00:08:00,220 --> 00:08:01,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I've had enough!</font>

75
00:08:01,620 --> 00:08:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you plotting?</font>

76
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I simply desire power!</font>

77
00:08:07,290 --> 00:08:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you read the forbidden scroll?</font>

78
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will pay for this!</font>

79
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The scroll was only forbidden so 
the royals could hog all the power!</font>

80
00:08:23,020 --> 00:08:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone help! Help!</font>

81
00:08:30,650 --> 00:08:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The blood of Vargr...</font>

82
00:08:34,710 --> 00:08:37,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selen, you're awake!</font>

83
00:08:38,110 --> 00:08:38,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness.</font>

84
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:41,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all right now.</font>

85
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother, I met the god Vargr.</font>

86
00:08:46,470 --> 00:08:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O great Vargr, thank you.</font>

87
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:56,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? No matter how much blood 
I drink, I'm still thirsty.</font>

88
00:08:57,090 --> 00:09:00,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the slightest bit of 
exposure to the sun...</font>

89
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:04,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I drank Vargr's blood, 
just like the princess.</font>

90
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:07,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I not drink enough? Is it 
because I lack shamanistic powers?</font>

91
00:09:08,310 --> 00:09:12,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If only I'd managed to read all of Vionys!</font>

92
00:09:12,930 --> 00:09:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why can't I become a perfect vampire?!</font>

93
00:09:20,130 --> 00:09:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, for certain...</font>

94
00:09:33,810 --> 00:09:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How come I'm stuck 
carrying everyone's crap?</font>

95
00:09:37,330 --> 00:09:39,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Cause you suck at rock-paper-scissors.</font>

96
00:09:41,730 --> 00:09:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

97
00:09:44,590 --> 00:09:45,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

98
00:09:49,390 --> 00:09:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mahan!</font>

99
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:57,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened? Where are Kamil and Ruslan?</font>

100
00:09:57,710 --> 00:09:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were caught.</font>

101
00:10:01,130 --> 00:10:04,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a bar called 
the Railgun in Printanier.</font>

102
00:10:05,190 --> 00:10:08,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We snuck in because we heard it 
was frequented by vampires.</font>

103
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:12,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it was a whole den of them.</font>

104
00:10:13,210 --> 00:10:15,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just when we thought we'd defeated them,</font>

105
00:10:16,230 --> 00:10:18,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he</i> showed up.</font>

106
00:10:24,020 --> 00:10:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I woke up, I was in some storeroom.</font>

107
00:10:31,410 --> 00:10:33,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kamil! Ruslan!</font>

108
00:10:37,990 --> 00:10:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A bunch of werewolves were trapped there.</font>

109
00:10:43,340 --> 00:10:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why?</font>

110
00:10:45,190 --> 00:10:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know exactly.</font>

111
00:10:47,990 --> 00:10:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I managed to escape, 
but I lost Kamil and Ruslan.</font>

112
00:10:53,620 --> 00:10:55,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not your fault.</font>

113
00:10:55,610 --> 00:10:57,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're glad you made it back.</font>

114
00:10:57,330 --> 00:11:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mahan, can you take us to that storeroom?</font>

115
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably.</font>

116
00:11:02,090 --> 00:11:03,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's head out right away.</font>

117
00:11:03,880 --> 00:11:06,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going to rescue Kamil and Ruslan.</font>

118
00:11:16,540 --> 00:11:17,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha!</font>

119
00:11:18,330 --> 00:11:19,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heli.</font>

120
00:11:26,830 --> 00:11:27,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha!</font>

121
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:32,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha! Are you okay?!</font>

122
00:11:33,810 --> 00:11:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The moon altar...</i></font>

123
00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

124
00:11:39,570 --> 00:11:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Take the sword to the moon altar...</i></font>

125
00:11:43,730 --> 00:11:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sword?</font>

126
00:11:47,850 --> 00:11:51,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha!</font>

127
00:11:53,890 --> 00:11:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just saw Sooha in a dream.</font>

128
00:11:57,100 --> 00:11:58,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too.</font>

129
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw her, too.</font>

130
00:11:59,810 --> 00:12:01,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was in a strange place.</font>

131
00:12:01,860 --> 00:12:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like a dark cave.</font>

132
00:12:05,410 --> 00:12:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was lying down.</font>

133
00:12:08,950 --> 00:12:12,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha mentioned a sword, didn't she?</font>

134
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Take the sword to the moon altar..."</font>

135
00:12:17,020 --> 00:12:20,980
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</b></font>

136
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:24,970
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</b></font>

137
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is it.</font>

138
00:12:39,750 --> 00:12:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jakah, can you sense Sooha's energy?</font>

139
00:12:42,570 --> 00:12:45,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. No trace of Marge's 
or Dardan's, either.</font>

140
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:48,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Vionys really here?</font>

141
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There must be a reason 
he had those matches.</font>

142
00:12:53,370 --> 00:12:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful, guys.</font>

143
00:12:55,420 --> 00:12:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something nearby.</font>

144
00:12:57,660 --> 00:13:01,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sense a massive amount 
of energy coming from it.</font>

145
00:13:01,460 --> 00:13:04,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's far beyond anything
we've encountered so far.</font>

146
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously? There's no one here.</font>

147
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are they not open?</font>

148
00:13:17,650 --> 00:13:19,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The door was unlocked, though.</font>

149
00:13:21,350 --> 00:13:22,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That way.</font>

150
00:13:23,090 --> 00:13:25,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's where his energy's coming from.</font>

151
00:13:36,620 --> 00:13:38,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A storeroom?</font>

152
00:13:43,420 --> 00:13:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't see a thing.</font>

153
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like the room is full of mist.</font>

154
00:13:53,980 --> 00:13:55,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're trapped!</font>

155
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:55,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

156
00:13:55,810 --> 00:13:57,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll give it a shot.</font>

157
00:14:00,130 --> 00:14:02,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the door won't open, 
I'll break it down.</font>

158
00:14:04,070 --> 00:14:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

159
00:14:06,020 --> 00:14:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel weak...</font>

160
00:14:11,230 --> 00:14:13,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something's off. I can't breathe...</font>

161
00:14:20,300 --> 00:14:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been waiting for you.</font>

162
00:14:23,430 --> 00:14:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew you'd come.</font>

163
00:14:27,170 --> 00:14:29,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is he?</font>

164
00:14:30,250 --> 00:14:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This mist isn't just for 
putting you to sleep.</font>

165
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:38,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll rob you of your strength, as well.</font>

166
00:14:38,290 --> 00:14:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guys, get outside!</font>

167
00:14:42,350 --> 00:14:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's open!</font>

168
00:15:01,450 --> 00:15:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once the moon is full, you will 
acquire all your power on this altar.</font>

169
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:12,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, it will all become mine.</font>

170
00:15:15,740 --> 00:15:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, you had the power, 
and I had my love.</font>

171
00:15:21,270 --> 00:15:23,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope it's the reverse this time.</font>

172
00:15:23,500 --> 00:15:27,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have the power, 
and you'll have love for me.</font>

173
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jaan, run!</font>

174
00:15:41,250 --> 00:15:42,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel weak...</i></font>

175
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:52,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn. I can't even transform.</font>

176
00:15:53,400 --> 00:15:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to defeat the guy 
controlling the mist.</font>

177
00:15:56,340 --> 00:15:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jakah, where is he?!</font>

178
00:16:06,930 --> 00:16:10,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're completely powerless now!</font>

179
00:16:17,010 --> 00:16:17,850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Heli.</i></font>

180
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:19,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Solon.</i></font>

181
00:16:21,340 --> 00:16:22,470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Shion.</i></font>

182
00:16:23,460 --> 00:16:24,500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Jino.</i></font>

183
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:26,760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Jaan.</i></font>

184
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:28,920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Jakah.</i></font>

185
00:16:29,990 --> 00:16:30,920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Noa.</i></font>

186
00:16:34,350 --> 00:16:35,560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Remember.</i></font>

187
00:16:40,370 --> 00:16:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now, you are vampire lords.</font>

188
00:17:30,690 --> 00:17:34,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How? How did they regain their power?!</font>

189
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it! In that case...</font>

190
00:17:39,850 --> 00:17:41,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mist got thicker!</font>

191
00:17:43,540 --> 00:17:46,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's that? Now you can't even move.</font>

192
00:17:48,510 --> 00:17:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotcha!</font>

193
00:17:49,520 --> 00:17:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're over here!</font>

194
00:18:12,850 --> 00:18:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mist is receding.</font>

195
00:18:17,700 --> 00:18:20,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? They all collapsed at once.</font>

196
00:18:20,670 --> 00:18:22,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it because we killed him?</font>

197
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He made those vampires by biting 
them, so their deaths were linked.</font>

198
00:18:27,710 --> 00:18:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is everyone okay?</font>

199
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

200
00:18:30,590 --> 00:18:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This thing appeared on my hand, 
and I regained consciousness.</font>

201
00:18:34,930 --> 00:18:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In fact, my body feels lighter than ever.</font>

202
00:18:38,850 --> 00:18:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel stronger, too.</font>

203
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:45,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moment this appeared, I became a wolf.</font>

204
00:18:45,420 --> 00:18:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think Sooha is helping us.</font>

205
00:18:52,330 --> 00:18:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's there?</font>

206
00:18:54,350 --> 00:18:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still alive.</font>

207
00:18:56,300 --> 00:18:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did your allies go?</font>

208
00:19:00,620 --> 00:19:03,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The royal palace...</font>

209
00:19:09,780 --> 00:19:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did he mean the ancient palace?</font>

210
00:19:12,300 --> 00:19:14,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that was a thousand years ago.</font>

211
00:19:14,910 --> 00:19:19,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is roughly where 
the palace used to be.</font>

212
00:19:21,340 --> 00:19:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Automnal, huh?</font>

213
00:19:23,570 --> 00:19:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">City hall was built on 
top of the palace ruins.</font>

214
00:19:33,580 --> 00:19:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sword.</font>

215
00:19:36,610 --> 00:19:40,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The last time I wielded that sword was 
when I fought Dardan in the palace.</font>

216
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe...</font>

217
00:19:51,080 --> 00:19:53,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our kin were being held in here.</font>

218
00:19:54,300 --> 00:19:55,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no one here.</font>

219
00:19:55,610 --> 00:19:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was this really the place?</font>

220
00:19:58,790 --> 00:20:01,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were all taken away.</font>

221
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:10,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This place is merely where 
the vampires keep us imprisoned.</font>

222
00:20:10,900 --> 00:20:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're ultimately put on boats 
and sent to a city called Automnal.</font>

223
00:20:17,170 --> 00:20:18,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you?</font>

224
00:20:18,150 --> 00:20:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A leftover.</font>

225
00:20:19,930 --> 00:20:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, they have 
no use for the elderly.</font>

226
00:20:23,870 --> 00:20:26,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happens to the ones 
who get sent to the city?</font>

227
00:20:27,180 --> 00:20:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know.</font>

228
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:34,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What I do know is that they're 
looking for a special wolf.</font>

229
00:20:35,170 --> 00:20:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A special wolf?</font>

230
00:20:39,750 --> 00:20:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan, the First Vampire, 
wants our kind's power.</font>

231
00:20:46,050 --> 00:20:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He needs that wolf's power to control us.</font>

232
00:20:56,710 --> 00:20:58,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They just keep coming.</font>

233
00:21:00,020 --> 00:21:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's no ordinary vampire!</font>

234
00:21:03,290 --> 00:21:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hit him with everything we've got!</font>

235
00:21:07,370 --> 00:21:08,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Him!</font>

236
00:21:09,260 --> 00:21:10,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That jerk...</font>

237
00:21:16,120 --> 00:21:19,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You. Where did you get that necklace?</font>

238
00:21:19,870 --> 00:21:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

239
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been passed down in 
my family for generations.</font>

240
00:21:24,520 --> 00:21:28,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is undoubtedly the 
mark of the Lycanthrope.</font>

241
00:21:29,110 --> 00:21:31,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lycanthrope?</font>

242
00:21:34,700 --> 00:21:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be...</font>

243
00:21:36,140 --> 00:21:39,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold on. I have no idea what you mean.</font>

244
00:21:39,770 --> 00:21:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lycanthropes are those who 
carry the blood of Vargr,</font>

245
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:47,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the wolf god of the ancient Vargr Kingdom.</font>

246
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are a werewolf chosen by a god.</font>

247
00:23:33,050 --> 00:23:39,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next time, Episode 10: 
"Waning Moon: Mortal Combat in Automnal."</i></font>

248
00:23:36,990 --> 00:23:40,250
<font face="Times New Roman" size="23" color="#f9fcfd"><b><font size="22">- Mortal Combat in Automnal -</font></b></font>

